<p class="text-after-table">You'll get half the refund amount if you paid a reduced fee ('remission').</p>

<h2 class="heading-medium">What you'll need</h2>

<ul class="list list-bullet">
    <li>About 10 minutes to complete the claim</li>
    <li>Name and date of birth of the donor</li>
